// Bubble Sort:    O(N²)    — never use
// Selection Sort: O(N²)    — never use
// Insertion Sort: O(N²)    — good for small/nearly sorted
// Merge Sort:     O(N logN) — stable guaranteed
// Quick Sort:     O(N logN) avg O(N²) worst — fastest in practice
